item.death_sword.manual_page_count=4
item.death_sword.manual_page_1=Sometimes you die. Death is a valid conception, no matter how strong.
item.death_sword.manual_page_2=Pawns can be slain easily, but consider a monster with 25535 health, what can your enchanted diamond sword do with it? Have you faced monsters with infinite health? I do. 
item.death_sword.manual_page_3=A sudden death for them is the solution, sudden death by INFINITE damage dealt. This is too powerful to be abused, so I bind it to the victims' fate. Stronger ones have a stronger fate to put out.  
item.death_sword.manual_page_4=With its full power released, it will kill targets at 100%% rate, but with a curse on it to kill its wielder at chance, so no tyrants can destroy the whole world with it, unless they... 
