item.power_triangle.manual_title=Triangle of Power
item.power_triangle.manual_author=Taoism DeepLake
item.power_triangle.manual_page_count=8
item.power_triangle.manual_page_1=Hold RMB to switch between Attack, Defense and Speed Mode. Pearls reduces mode cooldown and attack mode damage.
item.power_triangle.manual_page_2=I once met a little triangle, or a little boy, called Tico. In his world, geometric creatures are common.
item.power_triangle.manual_page_3=He had a interesting ability, which allowed him to transmute his health to mana, mana to aura, aura to health. He can not recover health and mana directly, but can do so with aura. 
item.power_triangle.manual_page_4=Therefore, when he is hurt, he transmutes his aura to health, and he is good as new. With a few transmutation, he will be at full status. In other words, status regnerates in turn.
item.power_triangle.manual_page_5=So I will create a pendant to transmute experience, hunger and health likewise? No. 
item.power_triangle.manual_page_5=I made something more straight forward: a pendant that can boost attack, defense and speed at choice, but only works in hand. I need a rest after making such a complicated whatnot. 
item.power_triangle.manual_page_6=When it functions as a sword, it costs durabilty on hit. When it works as a field-generator, it evaporates to provide the energy needed. Turn it to attack mode to prevent this waste, or just don't hold it.
item.power_triangle.manual_page_7=I wished it can boost all three aspects, but such a container won't hold such strong divine power. I broke many prototypes to learn that. All I can do is to carry three and rapidly switch them between hands.
item.power_triangle.manual_page_8=Then the idea hit me - what if I carry three of this at the same time? I tried a few time, and finally succeeded after many tries. It no longer need to be held to function, and the divine power eliminated the evaporation.

